Field_Notes: The eDNA record sheet for station M8 box 2 is not consistent with the CTD log sheet, which doesnt show an eDNA sample taken at M8 box 2. Based on the date (09/07/20) and the bottom depth (58m), and cross-referencing the CTD log I believe samples 5-8 were actually from DBO 1-5, and that I wrote M8 box 2 in error. Filter stored in 50cc tube.
